      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NITEONTHETOWN (1) made good progress when he raced parked but dug deep and scored by a head last week, adding to a strong record at this circuit and distance. Races well third-up and the ace draw gives him the chance to strike again. ANTIGUAS BE BE (3) came from this barrier to salute at this circuit and distance two runs back then his luck changed last time when he broke. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Big chance with manners. ZANY GIRL (6) draws wide but is racing well with a string of top-three finishes and she goes very well at this venue with two wins and a placing from three attempts. MACHETE ROULETTE (7) must be included on the back of some solid recent form, adding to a string of top-four finishes when third at Globe Derby on Saturday.",
